===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|亼|卩|ls=ic}}. The upper part is an open mouth to convey the idea of giving orders, while the bottom part is a kneeling man. Compare [[兄]], in which an open mouth on top of the character conveys the same idea of giving orders.

